We recently started to see the following LaTeX error on tokay2 (windows devel):

Package inputenc Error: Invalid UTF-8

We are not sure what exactly changed or was updated but the fix is relatively easy.

Please put

\usepackage[utf8]{inputenc}

at the beginning of your Sweave file right after the

\documentclass


The following packages have currently been identified but  please check your package build reports for tokay2 and if you see this ERROR please also correct:

BioNet
BioSeqClass
CSAR
DaMiRseq
GEOsubmission
GLAD
intansv
MOSim
OTUbase

We appreciate your assistance

Cheers,


